{"schema_version":"1.7.3","id":"GHSA-vw7g-jq9m-3q9v","published":"2020-09-02T18:23:35Z","modified":"2020-08-31T18:36:38Z","summary":"Unauthorized File Access in glance","details":"Versions of `glance` prior to 3.0.7 are vulnerable to Unauthorized File Access. The package provides a `--nodot` option meant to hide files and directories with names that begin with a `.`, such as `.git` but fails to hide files inside a folder that begins with `.`. \n\n\n## Recommendation\n\nUpgrade to version 3.0.7 or later.","affected":[{"package":{"name":"glance","ecosystem":"npm","purl":"pkg:npm/glance"},"ranges":[{"type":"SEMVER","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"3.0.7"}]}],"database_specific":{"source":"https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/main/advisories/github-reviewed/2020/09/GHSA-vw7g-jq9m-3q9v/GHSA-vw7g-jq9m-3q9v.json"}}],"references":[{"type":"WEB","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/490379"},{"type":"WEB","url":"https://www.npmjs.com/advisories/811"}],"database_specific":{"cwe_ids":[],"github_reviewed":true,"github_reviewed_at":"2020-08-31T18:36:38Z","nvd_published_at":null,"severity":"MODERATE"}}